  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      rituximab and modified (hyperCVAD) administered every 28 days for 4-6 cycles followed by
      rituximab maintenance therapy consisting of four weekly doses every six months for two years
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
